# Panels - endpoints de ejemplo

### Obtener todos los paneles
GET http://localhost:4000/api/paneles
Accept: application/json

### Obtener panel por id
GET http://localhost:4000/api/panel/1
Accept: application/json

### Crear panel (ejemplo)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/paneles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Panel Basico",
  "description": "Paquete de pruebas basicas",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}
# Paneles API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@authToken = {{authToken}}

## Rutas publicas

### Crear panel (publico)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/panel/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Panel Basico",
  "description": "Paquete de pruebas basicas",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar paneles (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paneles/public
Accept: application/json

### Obtener panel por id (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/panel/1/public
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar panel (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/panel/1/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Paquete de pruebas basicas actualizado",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar panel fisicamente (publico)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/panel/1/public

### Baja logica de panel (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/panel/1/logic/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

## Rutas protegidas (requieren token)

### Crear panel (con auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/panel
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Panel Avanzado",
  "description": "Panel con pruebas especializadas",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar paneles (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/paneles
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtener panel por id (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/panel/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar panel (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/panel/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Panel especializado actualizado",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar panel fisicamente (con auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/panel/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Baja logica de panel (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/panel/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}
